I’ll talk before and then at the time you
can just tell me what time it is.

2
00:00:15,764 --> 00:00:22,542
The radio is off? You can keep it till
eight o’clock and…

3
00:00:42,169 --> 00:00:45,940
So happy to wait on you.

4
00:00:52,758 --> 00:00:58,936
Today we are celebrating a day

5
00:01:01,436 --> 00:01:06,678
which is a very, very important,

6
00:01:06,894 --> 00:01:12,588
absolutely the most important, we can say,
day,

7
00:01:12,789 --> 00:01:19,346
when such a great happening took
place.

8
00:01:20,417 --> 00:01:25,161
And it had to take place that way –

9
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:32,090
it was all in a way destined.

10
00:01:41,211 --> 00:01:45,809
In my last lectures I have told you

11
00:01:46,010 --> 00:01:54,734
how Christ was created first
in the heavens.

12
00:01:56,389 --> 00:02:05,980
In the Devi Mahatmya, if you read that,
He was created as Mahavishnu

13
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:16,280
and is mentioned very clearly, that first
He was created as an egg.

14
00:02:16,604 --> 00:02:23,784
It is written in this book, which perhaps
was written about 14,000 years back.

15
00:02:24,496 --> 00:02:29,059
It’s a book that predicts about Christ,

16
00:02:30,365 --> 00:02:35,247
and that is why people in the West,
specially,

17
00:02:35,448 --> 00:02:38,964
offer an egg to each other as a friend.

18
00:02:39,165 --> 00:02:45,256
The first existence came on this Earth
as an egg, that was Christ,

19
00:02:45,457 --> 00:03:00,056
and part of it was kept in that state
and the rest of it was used

20
00:03:01,062 --> 00:03:10,502
by the Holy Ghost, by Mahalakshmi,
to create Christ out of it.

21
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:16,306
In that ancient book He was called
as Mahavishnu;

22
00:03:16,507 --> 00:03:19,626
means the greater form of Vishnu.

23
00:03:19,827 --> 00:03:22,860
But actually Vishnu is the father

24
00:03:23,061 --> 00:03:28,923
and He is the Son created by the Holy
Ghost.

25
00:03:29,124 --> 00:03:33,880
After my lecture I would like, if you have
the book, to read it out to them,

26
00:03:34,081 --> 00:03:39,023
the whole texts of how Christ was created.

27
00:03:40,062 --> 00:03:48,806
And when He was created, He cried
for His Father,

28
00:03:50,466 --> 00:03:54,362
as He cried also on the cross once.

29
00:03:54,960 --> 00:04:01,047
And He cried for years.

30
00:04:02,709 --> 00:04:09,187
And then Christ, in Mahavishnu state
was blessed by His Father

31
00:04:09,388 --> 00:04:14,407
who said that, “Your position will be
placed higher than Mine.

32
00:04:14,608 --> 00:04:18,420
And You will be the Adhara,” means
the ‘Support of the Universe’.

33
00:04:18,621 --> 00:04:24,166
See, how from Mooladhara He becomes
the Adhara.

34
00:04:27,495 --> 00:04:32,566
This was all done at the heavenly stage -

35
00:04:32,775 --> 00:04:36,531
Vaikuntha stage you can say.

36
00:04:37,323 --> 00:04:43,272
Then He was given birth by the Holy Ghost,

37
00:04:43,473 --> 00:04:48,443
who was the mother of Christ on this
Earth,

38
00:04:48,644 --> 00:04:54,936
who was nobody else but was the incarnation
of Mahalakshmi; means She was Radha.

39
00:04:55,137 --> 00:05:01,420
Ra-dha. ‘Ra’ means energy, ‘dha’ means
the one who sustains the energy.

40
00:05:06,107 --> 00:05:11,272
There are many aspects of Easter one
has to understand,

41
00:05:12,536 --> 00:05:18,920
but the most of all is why did He die and
why was He resurrected?

42
00:05:19,121 --> 00:05:24,189
This point I have not yet touched, perhaps,
so clearly.

43
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:27,663
That’s the point I want to tell you today.

44
00:05:27,864 --> 00:05:32,273
It’s only you people can understand
the importance of the life of Christ.

45
00:05:32,474 --> 00:05:41,206
And when it is said that you have to get
your realisation through Christ,

46
00:05:41,407 --> 00:05:46,734
it means that He had to pierce through
the Agnya chakra.

47
00:05:46,972 --> 00:05:52,351
He had to be there. If He had not created

48
00:05:52,552 --> 00:05:58,169
this gap in the gate, we could never have
got realisation.

49
00:05:58,370 --> 00:06:04,956
That is why it is said that you are to pass
through

50
00:06:05,157 --> 00:06:14,254
the gates of heaven only with the grace
of Christ.

51
00:06:14,624 --> 00:06:17,482
Of course, that doesn’t mean churches,
it doesn’t mean at all churches.

52
00:06:17,683 --> 00:06:21,091
That you understand as sahaja yogis that
you have to pass through the Agnya chakra.

53
00:06:21,292 --> 00:06:26,340
Ultimately that’s the most difficult point
where human beings have to pass.

54
00:06:26,541 --> 00:06:34,326
Because, at the Agnya chakra, your ego
and superego are fully grown.

55
00:06:34,527 --> 00:06:38,786
At the human stage only this ego
is developed.

56
00:06:38,987 --> 00:06:43,368
Now how to overcome the ego was a point.

57
00:06:43,569 --> 00:06:50,574
And to overcome the ego, Christ had
to do this.

58
00:06:51,249 --> 00:06:57,837
When He was created in the beginning
as Shri Ganesha -

59
00:06:58,837 --> 00:07:07,396
you know the story how He was created,
that the mala,

60
00:07:07,597 --> 00:07:18,008
is the - from the body of Parvati, the Holy
Ghost, was taken out,

61
00:07:18,209 --> 00:07:24,816
because before Her marriage, She was -

62
00:07:25,017 --> 00:07:32,521
She had to cover Herself for Her bath
with many scented things.

63
00:07:32,722 --> 00:07:37,726
And it was taken out, all these things,
and Her vibrations came out.

64
00:07:37,927 --> 00:07:41,748
And She created this child just to protect
Her chastity;

65
00:07:41,949 --> 00:07:47,664
outside Her bathroom She put him. And
you know the whole story about it.

66
00:07:47,865 --> 00:07:53,725
Now there was a part of the element
of the earth in that child.

67
00:07:53,926 --> 00:07:57,595
Pruthvi-tattwa, was there.

68
00:07:57,796 --> 00:08:09,458
All other centres - all other centres have
got some elements in them.

69
00:08:09,659 --> 00:08:15,291
Some elements like pruthvi-tattwa is there,
earth element;

70
00:08:15,492 --> 00:08:20,335
then you have got water element, then
you have got air element,

71
00:08:20,536 --> 00:08:29,696
and when you come to this it is the light
element, it’s the light.

72
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:36,051
And at this point, at Agnya chakra,

73
00:08:36,357 --> 00:08:42,160
He had to cross the last element, that
was the light element.

74
00:08:42,361 --> 00:08:46,424
That means He had to come out into
the true form

75
00:08:46,625 --> 00:08:55,204
of only the Divine Power, the Omkara,
the vibrations you can call it;

76
00:08:55,405 --> 00:09:03,237
or the absolute -

77
00:09:03,438 --> 00:09:08,227
you call it logos or something like that?
The first sound, Brahma.

78
00:09:08,428 --> 00:09:11,739
So He had to become the principle
of Brahma.

79
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:13,662
To become the principle of Brahma,

80
00:09:13,863 --> 00:09:18,706
He had to get rid of all other elements
within Him.

81
00:09:18,907 --> 00:09:25,124
So the last was also the light element,
which He had to cross through.

82
00:09:25,325 --> 00:09:30,359
So He had earth element in Him, as He
was of the mala,

83
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:35,534
and all other elements within Him.
But when it comes to the Agnya,

84
00:09:35,735 --> 00:09:39,392
He had to give up all the elements,
that He had to die

85
00:09:39,593 --> 00:09:42,375
the death of all these elements that were
within Him,

86
00:09:42,576 --> 00:09:47,819
to become complete, absolutely pure
Spirit.

87
00:09:50,391 --> 00:09:56,081
What He did on subtle form works out
on the gross form,

88
00:09:57,174 --> 00:10:04,850
and to do that He had to die. And
whatever died in Him,

89
00:10:05,051 --> 00:10:08,221
was that little element of earth element
and other elements,

90
00:10:08,422 --> 00:10:13,063
and what came out of Him was pure Spirit.

91
00:10:13,264 --> 00:10:16,123
[To somebody: “Just move forward.”]

92
00:10:16,324 --> 00:10:21,265
Was pure Spirit that was resurrected;
the pure Spirit,

93
00:10:21,466 --> 00:10:28,543
the pure Brahma-Tattwa which had formed
the body of Christ,

94
00:10:28,744 --> 00:10:32,922
which was the body of Christ.

95
00:10:35,705 --> 00:10:39,738
And this happening came -

96
00:10:39,939 --> 00:10:47,247
Christ has done what was predicted
about Him -

97
00:10:47,747 --> 00:10:54,506
that He is the saviour, because He passed
through that gate

98
00:10:54,707 --> 00:10:59,872
to take people from this bodily existence,

99
00:11:00,073 --> 00:11:06,289
means the one that depends on the elements,

100
00:11:06,490 --> 00:11:10,094
to that existence which is Spirit.

101
00:11:10,295 --> 00:11:17,586
So the resurrection is where you become,
from your attention,

102
00:11:17,787 --> 00:11:22,393
you jump into the attention of the Spirit.

103
00:11:22,594 --> 00:11:29,916
When you feel your attention, when you
become the Spirit.

104
00:11:30,117 --> 00:11:38,322
That is the happening which has happened
to you also.

105
00:11:38,523 --> 00:11:45,155
But He became pure Spirit, pure Brahma
Tattwa when He was resurrected.

106
00:11:45,356 --> 00:11:54,729
And the resurrection is a happening
of the Divine Power

107
00:11:54,930 --> 00:12:04,413
which came from Mooladhara chakra as just
earth element, started growing.

108
00:12:04,614 --> 00:12:08,854
It took its birth from there, came up
to Agnya chakra.

109
00:12:09,055 --> 00:12:17,250
There Christ was created to pass through
all the elements,

110
00:12:17,451 --> 00:12:22,660
ultimately to enter into the Sahasrara

111
00:12:22,861 --> 00:12:28,321
to become a complete Brahma Tattwa.

112
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:39,999
And this was a very difficult thing,
was very experimental.

113
00:12:40,208 --> 00:12:45,849
And the experiment was quite a dangerous
one.

114
00:12:47,391 --> 00:12:54,085
It could have failed also, because He had
in Him

115
00:12:54,317 --> 00:13:01,682
that human element, the body element
which suffered.

116
00:13:03,009 --> 00:13:09,118
And He suffered, because this body element
suffers, not the Spirit;

117
00:13:09,319 --> 00:13:13,154
Spirit does not suffer. The body element
suffers.

118
00:13:13,363 --> 00:13:23,532
So He had to suffer that body element
and to get over it, to get out of it.

119
00:13:25,339 --> 00:13:36,950
And to get out of it He had to have
a tremendous courage.

120
00:13:38,071 --> 00:13:43,378
It was such a difficult operation.

121
00:13:44,132 --> 00:13:47,706
Without Him nobody could have achieved.

122
00:13:47,907 --> 00:13:50,931
He knew it was predestined,

123
00:13:51,132 --> 00:13:58,765
but it was one of the most difficult things
to happen.

124
00:13:58,966 --> 00:14:05,002
I wonder how many Christians know
the significance of an egg.

125
00:14:05,203 --> 00:14:13,471
Now egg signifies a stage where you are
before realisation,

126
00:14:13,672 --> 00:14:20,987
when you are in your eggshell; that you
are Mr. X, you are Mrs. Y, all that.

127
00:14:21,188 --> 00:14:25,367
But when you mature fully inside,

128
00:14:25,568 --> 00:14:30,781
the bird is ready and that is the time
you are hatched.

129
00:14:30,982 --> 00:14:34,541
This is the time you get twice born.

130
00:14:34,742 --> 00:14:39,372
So, actually the resurrection of Christ
signifies that,

131
00:14:39,573 --> 00:14:45,276
and that’s why we give that egg to people
saying,

132
00:14:45,477 --> 00:14:52,202
“You are an egg”, a reminder of that, and
this egg can become the Spirit.

133
00:14:52,403 --> 00:14:56,700
And also it is written that it was an egg
when He came.

134
00:14:56,901 --> 00:15:03,993
First He was created as an egg. Half of it
remained as Shri Ganesha

135
00:15:04,194 --> 00:15:08,368
and half of it became Mahavishnu.

136
00:15:08,569 --> 00:15:14,429
Then He came on this earth and He departed
with all His elements

137
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:19,272
and the pure vibrations formed His body,

138
00:15:19,473 --> 00:15:27,534
and He remained there within all of you,
to be awakened.

139
00:15:27,735 --> 00:15:35,591
And when the Kundalini takes your attention
through that point,

140
00:15:35,792 --> 00:15:40,265
there you also become the Spirit.

141
00:15:40,589 --> 00:15:45,372
That’s why He said that, “I’m the gate,
I’m the door.”

142
00:15:45,573 --> 00:15:50,309
He didn’t say, “I’m the destination.”
He said, “I’m the door,”

143
00:15:50,510 --> 00:15:54,069
because you cannot become Christ.

144
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:57,866
That’s why he didn’t say, “I’m the
destination,” that you have to achieve Him.

145
00:15:58,067 --> 00:16:03,499
But He has created this space for you.

146
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:11,890
You can become spiritually awakened;
you can become your Spirit.

147
00:16:12,099 --> 00:16:17,617
But Christ is an incarnation, He was
the Son of God.

148
00:16:17,818 --> 00:16:23,380
And so He is an incarnation, and that
incarnation came on this earth

149
00:16:23,581 --> 00:16:32,378
just to pull you out of your elements,
to make you become the Spirit.

150
00:16:32,604 --> 00:16:39,284
Now how is it that it was the most
difficult thing?

151
00:16:39,485 --> 00:16:47,085
Because human beings have created in their
heads all kinds of artificial barriers.

152
00:16:47,286 --> 00:16:50,760
You see, whatever we think and whatever
we do with our mind

153
00:16:50,961 --> 00:16:54,769
is all dead, is man-made, is artificial.

154
00:16:54,970 --> 00:17:00,457
Because reality is beyond your mind;
it is not in your mind.

155
00:17:00,658 --> 00:17:03,151
You cannot conceive it; you cannot hold it.

156
00:17:03,352 --> 00:17:08,704
Whatever is in your mind is not
the reality, it is beyond.

157
00:17:08,905 --> 00:17:14,853
So, for a human being to accept something
that is beyond mind

158
00:17:15,054 --> 00:17:17,328
had become so difficult at the time
of Christ,

159
00:17:17,529 --> 00:17:19,994
because of Romans and all these people
coming up.

160
00:17:20,195 --> 00:17:23,770
And we are repeating the history again.

161
00:17:24,119 --> 00:17:27,574
They were so ego-oriented, they were
so full of ego

162
00:17:27,775 --> 00:17:37,246
that to destroy their ego somebody had
to do this to create a passage.

163
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:43,677
By His death so many things are proved,
that all those who crucified Him

164
00:17:43,878 --> 00:17:47,707
were stupid people, they were ego-oriented,
they were blind.

165
00:17:47,908 --> 00:17:51,154
They could not see what He was.

166
00:17:51,355 --> 00:17:56,920
They could not see what a genuine
personality He was.

167
00:17:57,121 --> 00:18:00,960
They crucified Him.

168
00:18:03,183 --> 00:18:07,847
I mean, it’s the greatest stupidity. And
they crucified Him,

169
00:18:08,048 --> 00:18:11,438
it was all known because these people
were so stupid

170
00:18:11,639 --> 00:18:15,014
that they would have only crucified Him,
what else they could do?

171
00:18:15,238 --> 00:18:19,691
Because they couldn’t bear, with their
little egos, somebody who is so simple,

172
00:18:19,892 --> 00:18:23,029
who is so genuine, who is so true.

173
00:18:23,230 --> 00:18:32,015
So they crucified Him and that crucifixion
came as a breakthrough for us.

174
00:18:32,216 --> 00:18:36,257
But message for us is the resurrection
part.

175
00:18:36,458 --> 00:18:41,492
Message for us is the resurrection, and
not crucifixion.

176
00:18:41,693 --> 00:18:45,561
Crucifixion is not the message, because
He’s done it for us.

177
00:18:45,762 --> 00:18:51,539
This is the point where Jews must
understand.

178
00:18:52,284 --> 00:18:55,842
The other day I was reading - today only -

179
00:18:56,043 --> 00:19:04,104
some discussion with the Archbishop
of Canterbury took place.

180
00:19:04,305 --> 00:19:08,752
And the fellow who was asking him was
asking him questions

181
00:19:08,953 --> 00:19:13,682
as if he was asking questions to God.

182
00:19:14,616 --> 00:19:18,780
In a way he said so also that, “I would
ask this question to God,

183
00:19:18,981 --> 00:19:22,401
that, why is it so many Jews were killed?”

184
00:19:22,602 --> 00:19:25,317
They asked for it.

185
00:19:25,518 --> 00:19:29,751
They wanted that they must suffer

186
00:19:29,952 --> 00:19:33,366
because they wouldn’t give the credit
of suffering to Christ.

187
00:19:33,567 --> 00:19:37,061
They thought, “We all have to suffer.”
Ego. It’s ego.

188
00:19:37,262 --> 00:19:42,409
“How dare anybody suffer for us? We must
suffer separately.”

189
00:19:43,259 --> 00:19:44,710
They couldn’t give that credit to Christ

190
00:19:44,910 --> 00:19:52,981
and all the later thinking was that,
“We must suffer.”

191
00:19:53,182 --> 00:20:01,261
So, whatever you think, comes into action
on this gross level,

192
00:20:01,462 --> 00:20:06,753
so Mr. Hitler was born and he made them
suffer.

193
00:20:10,427 --> 00:20:18,285
And the stupidity of human beings
is responsible

194
00:20:18,486 --> 00:20:23,481
for all the problems that are created
on this earth.

195
00:20:23,682 --> 00:20:26,430
The other question was, “How the children
get leukemia?”

196
00:20:26,631 --> 00:20:28,423
He would ask God, “How children get it?”

197
00:20:28,624 --> 00:20:34,330
If the parents are so frantic and speedy,
children have to get it.

198
00:20:35,459 --> 00:20:40,192
If you are not relaxed person when you
are married

199
00:20:40,393 --> 00:20:44,020
and when you are going to have a baby,
you are thinking of divorces

200
00:20:44,221 --> 00:20:48,271
and all sorts of nonsense, that franticness
will work on the child.

201
00:20:48,472 --> 00:20:51,569
Psychologically it is a left-side problem,
and the child has to be

202
00:20:51,770 --> 00:20:59,370
a patient of leukemia as soon as he is
born. That is what it is.

203
00:21:03,384 --> 00:21:10,992
So the problems are created by human beings
because of their stupidity.

204
00:21:11,193 --> 00:21:13,988
There is no problem that God has created
for you.

205
00:21:14,189 --> 00:21:17,627
He’s solved all your problems. All your
problems He solves;

206
00:21:17,828 --> 00:21:21,773
you have seen in Sahaj Yoga how He solves
your little, little problems even.

207
00:21:21,974 --> 00:21:27,750
But we create problems for ourselves
by our stupidity,

208
00:21:27,951 --> 00:21:38,039
by our addiction to elements, to material
things,

209
00:21:38,494 --> 00:21:43,466
to material habits. Matter sits on our
head.

210
00:21:47,272 --> 00:21:58,084
That is on the, we can say, on the level
of the earth element.

211
00:21:59,363 --> 00:22:04,437
Then we have other problems like
emotional attachments:

212
00:22:04,638 --> 00:22:07,992
“This is my daughter; this is my child;
this is my; this is mine;

213
00:22:08,193 --> 00:22:11,867
I’m so attached to my child.”

214
00:22:14,825 --> 00:22:19,349
Then, “This is my country. This is your
country.”

215
00:22:19,550 --> 00:22:23,330
We create problem. This Falkland camp...
Falkland this thing

216
00:22:23,531 --> 00:22:26,914
is an artificial problem, you can see
that.

217
00:22:27,115 --> 00:22:30,147
I mean, when these people went there,
these Spaniards,

218
00:22:30,348 --> 00:22:32,961
they all should be driven back to Spain.

219
00:22:33,162 --> 00:22:37,902
And all from Brazil should be driven back
to Portugal.

220
00:22:38,103 --> 00:22:42,510
What are they doing there if this is
the situation?

221
00:22:42,711 --> 00:22:46,531
But they are all human beings! What is
this territory business?

222
00:22:46,732 --> 00:22:50,161
So let human beings live happily wherever
they are.

223
00:22:50,362 --> 00:22:53,053
What are they going to get out of this
territory?

224
00:22:53,254 --> 00:22:57,558
God never created Argentina, Chile, England
and all that,

225
00:22:57,759 --> 00:23:03,461
He created one homogeneous structure,
and it is to look after each other.

226
00:23:03,662 --> 00:23:06,448
Like a heart is created, a liver is
created,

227
00:23:06,649 --> 00:23:09,689
a brain is created, a nose is created.

228
00:23:09,890 --> 00:23:14,758
If they start fighting - say this eye
starts fighting this eye.

229
00:23:14,959 --> 00:23:20,324
We laugh, but we human beings do the same
thing.

230
00:23:21,147 --> 00:23:23,616
We are all the time doing like this.

231
00:23:23,817 --> 00:23:29,885
This is the stupidity of human beings,
which is creating problem.

232
00:23:30,086 --> 00:23:33,071
And when you become very stupid,
somebody horrible

233
00:23:33,272 --> 00:23:36,176
takes advantage of that and comes
on this earth

234
00:23:36,377 --> 00:23:43,070
just like Hitler, and he tries to put you
right.

235
00:23:43,648 --> 00:23:49,993
You don’t need all that. You need only
wisdom and your realisation.

236
00:23:50,194 --> 00:23:54,025
And that is what is done today that you
have got realisation.

237
00:23:54,226 --> 00:24:00,870
So Easter for sahaj yogis all over
the world, is the most important happening,

238
00:24:01,071 --> 00:24:04,878
because if it had not happened it would
not have been possible

239
00:24:05,079 --> 00:24:08,395
to give realisation to people.

240
00:24:12,409 --> 00:24:14,766
I think Gavin will read it out to you
later on

241
00:24:14,967 --> 00:24:18,444
about what is written about Christ in Devi
Mahatmya.

242
00:24:18,645 --> 00:24:23,331
This book was written about 14,000 years
back by Markandeya.

243
00:24:23,532 --> 00:24:29,012
So imagine, 14,000 years back he knew,
being a seer, just like Blake,

244
00:24:29,213 --> 00:24:33,825
what was going to happen when Christ
was to come.

245
00:24:34,026 --> 00:24:36,638
But He was called as Mahavishnu. He was
not Vishnu,

246
00:24:36,839 --> 00:24:40,025
He was the son of Vishnu.

247
00:24:43,355 --> 00:24:51,234
And how many Christians understand about
Easter? They don’t.

248
00:24:51,435 --> 00:24:54,612
They - it’s - Christianity today is nothing
but a mental activity,

249
00:24:54,813 --> 00:24:57,255
that’s all, which is dead; nonsense it is.

250
00:24:57,456 --> 00:24:59,821
Just like any other nonsensical religion,
it has become

251
00:25:00,022 --> 00:25:04,340
another foolish, stupid religion, which has
no meaning.

252
00:25:04,541 --> 00:25:08,361
Unless and until you get your realisation,
unless and until you feel the vibrations,

253
00:25:08,562 --> 00:25:13,232
unless and until you feel this Divine
Surrounding Power, how will you understand?

254
00:25:13,433 --> 00:25:15,409
Because that’s the only thing that is
truth;

255
00:25:15,610 --> 00:25:18,380
that’s the only thing that is reality,

256
00:25:18,581 --> 00:25:22,972
and unless and until you achieve it, how
will you know about Christ?

257
00:25:23,173 --> 00:25:27,421
And fighting about Him; how can you fight?
I can’t understand really.

258
00:25:27,622 --> 00:25:33,152
To me, it’s stupidity gone to another
extreme.

259
00:25:33,691 --> 00:25:37,439
By this thing, what you do actually,
is to use

260
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:42,389
all these great incarnations to kill each
other. Can you imagine?

261
00:25:42,590 --> 00:25:46,972
The things that came to elevate you,
to make you into higher living

262
00:25:47,173 --> 00:25:50,742
are now used, the same things, the names
are used

263
00:25:50,943 --> 00:25:53,679
to kill each other, to bring down each
other.

264
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:57,204
At the most, if you reach a point where
you don’t understand,

265
00:25:57,405 --> 00:26:01,122
then they start saying, “It’s a mystery.”

266
00:26:01,323 --> 00:26:04,563
What is the mystery? In Sahaj Yoga
there’s no mystery.

267
00:26:04,764 --> 00:26:08,986
It’s all just there.

268
00:26:09,435 --> 00:26:13,672
To me, human beings are a mystery.

269
00:26:13,873 --> 00:26:18,704
I don’t understand them. I can’t
understand.

270
00:26:18,905 --> 00:26:25,427
The resurrection of Christ has to now be
collective resurrection.

271
00:26:25,628 --> 00:26:33,109
This is what is Maha Yoga. Has to be
the collective resurrection

272
00:26:33,310 --> 00:26:35,589
and for this collective resurrection,

273
00:26:35,790 --> 00:26:40,283
first of all sahaj yogis must decide to be
collective.

274
00:26:40,484 --> 00:26:47,234
Because through Kundalini awakening,
you cross, no doubt, you cross through,

275
00:26:47,435 --> 00:26:52,717
but you enter an area of collectivity.

276
00:26:52,918 --> 00:26:58,453
And if you do not allow that collectivity
to permeate into you,

277
00:26:58,654 --> 00:27:01,178
then you come down.

278
00:27:01,379 --> 00:27:07,082
Supposing you become a state beyond
the element,

279
00:27:07,283 --> 00:27:10,641
the state where you are a collective being;

280
00:27:10,842 --> 00:27:13,366
you are aware of the collective being;

281
00:27:13,567 --> 00:27:16,924
you are aware that you are a part and
parcel of the whole;

282
00:27:17,125 --> 00:27:21,654
you are aware that you have to help
your nose and your eyes

283
00:27:21,855 --> 00:27:24,187
because you are part and parcel
of the whole.

284
00:27:24,388 --> 00:27:27,112
You reach that stage where you understand
that,

285
00:27:27,313 --> 00:27:32,216
“I am as important as other cells are, and
other cells are to be helped by me

286
00:27:32,417 --> 00:27:36,613
and they have to sustain me, we are one.”
There should be complete concord.

287
00:27:36,814 --> 00:27:42,587
This awareness comes after realisation,
and if you do not understand

288
00:27:42,788 --> 00:27:47,419
that this awareness, that this collective
awareness

289
00:27:47,620 --> 00:27:53,417
is the only way you can stay in that area.
Otherwise you get out.

290
00:27:53,618 --> 00:28:03,743
You start having your smaller wells and
you just go down into them.

291
00:28:04,724 --> 00:28:09,481
The more you start to expand yourself,
you rise higher

292
00:28:09,698 --> 00:28:14,501
and then you are again with your badhas
or whatever it is.

293
00:28:14,702 --> 00:28:19,150
But if you think that, “I have to live
for the whole.

294
00:28:19,351 --> 00:28:26,181
I’m responsible for the whole. I’m
responsible for creating

295
00:28:26,577 --> 00:28:32,529
a nucleus of a cell which is going to look
after the whole,

296
00:28:32,730 --> 00:28:35,557
and if I fall down the rest also suffers.

297
00:28:35,758 --> 00:28:40,982
I have no business to fall down because
I have been resurrected to this point.

298
00:28:41,183 --> 00:28:46,751
I have entered into the state of
collectivity, where my being,

299
00:28:46,952 --> 00:28:50,300
which is the Spirit, is the collective
being

300
00:28:50,501 --> 00:28:53,543
and I have to stay there, I have to be
there;

301
00:28:53,744 --> 00:28:58,219
I cannot fall, it’s not the way I can
live.”

302
00:28:58,443 --> 00:29:03,522
But I have seen after realisation also,
people cannot get out of their shells.

303
00:29:03,723 --> 00:29:08,758
They still remain in the shell. They cannot
spread their wings

304
00:29:08,959 --> 00:29:16,531
and sing, and get out of their shell and
just fly.

305
00:29:16,732 --> 00:29:21,764
They cannot do it. They still stick on to
their small ways of life,

306
00:29:21,965 --> 00:29:24,780
in a smaller ways, in every way.

307
00:29:24,981 --> 00:29:29,590
In a holiday you go, you want to have
a separate holiday. Why?

308
00:29:29,791 --> 00:29:33,200
This is the holiday time, holy-day as they
say.

309
00:29:33,401 --> 00:29:38,132
Holy day. This is the holy-day. When you
are with other sahaja yogis

310
00:29:38,333 --> 00:29:42,827
you are really enjoying the holiday. Where
do you enjoy a holiday otherwise?

311
00:29:43,028 --> 00:29:48,623
Which is the other way? To be with them
is the real holiday.

312
00:29:49,107 --> 00:29:54,953
And that is why one should understand that
you should expand your collectivity.

313
00:29:55,154 --> 00:29:58,474
If you do not expand your collectivity
you are just a waste.

314
00:29:58,675 --> 00:30:02,931
You are a wasteful creation of sahaj yogis,

315
00:30:03,132 --> 00:30:06,918
which I’m sorry to say, will go down.

316
00:30:07,119 --> 00:30:09,189
Such people show also, in the beginning,

317
00:30:09,390 --> 00:30:13,691
gradually they start getting better and
better and better.

318
00:30:13,892 --> 00:30:16,518
And once you are there in full state,
you really enjoy each

319
00:30:16,719 --> 00:30:19,191
other’s company without having any fears
about them,

320
00:30:19,392 --> 00:30:21,629
without having any possessiveness about
them,

321
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:28,446
without having any kind of expectation,
but just enjoying each other.

322
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:34,546
That has to happen. Like all our cells
in our body are like that.

323
00:30:34,747 --> 00:30:42,381
If they can do it, why not we? Because
we have so much of sense;

324
00:30:42,582 --> 00:30:46,241
at least we think we have more sense
than the cells have.

325
00:30:46,442 --> 00:30:49,206
At least it is expected, because we have
evolved so much

326
00:30:49,407 --> 00:30:52,019
from a unicell to this state.

327
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:56,603
And then you are the epitome of God’s
creation;

328
00:30:56,804 --> 00:31:00,249
you are the topmost people. Then why not?

329
00:31:00,450 --> 00:31:03,547
When you are resurrected, the first thing
that should happen to you

330
00:31:03,748 --> 00:31:07,304
is to understand that you are no more
an individual,

331
00:31:07,505 --> 00:31:11,634
but you are a collective being. You are
no more an individual.

332
00:31:11,857 --> 00:31:21,223
All things which make you circumcise
your individuality - throw that away.

333
00:31:21,952 --> 00:31:25,240
You are no more an individual. All problems
which come to you

334
00:31:25,441 --> 00:31:34,340
as individual problems are absolutely
useless, false, wasteful.

335
00:31:34,541 --> 00:31:39,465
Think of the collective problems. I enjoy
such people.

336
00:31:39,666 --> 00:31:44,964
Like the other day Fergie was anxious
to know about Bristol -

337
00:31:45,165 --> 00:31:50,413
which points are there, which are giving
vibrations from the Mother Earth.

338
00:31:50,614 --> 00:31:53,759
He’s worried about the whole of Bristol -
all the Jamaicans,

339
00:31:53,960 --> 00:31:59,288
then about the whole Britain - British
people,

340
00:31:59,489 --> 00:32:03,283
and then of the whole world you should be.
That’s what one should think.

341
00:32:03,484 --> 00:32:06,731
One should not think, “How will my daughter
get married?

342
00:32:06,932 --> 00:32:09,084
How can I get a ticket to go there?”

343
00:32:09,285 --> 00:32:11,656
All these nonsensical ideas should be
given up

344
00:32:11,857 --> 00:32:14,955
because you are now entered into
the Kingdom of God

345
00:32:15,156 --> 00:32:18,222
and He is going to look after you.

346
00:32:18,452 --> 00:32:23,170
Because that state you establish within
yourself that you are a collective being.

347
00:32:23,371 --> 00:32:26,927
All other things will drop out. Gradually
everybody will be molded.

348
00:32:27,128 --> 00:32:32,067
Even the most difficult I have seen,
have improved.

349
00:32:32,268 --> 00:32:35,469
But what about you, the one who is
improving everybody else,

350
00:32:35,670 --> 00:32:38,472
what about you? How far you are there?

351
00:32:38,673 --> 00:32:41,714
How far in your faith that you know that,

352
00:32:41,915 --> 00:32:44,995
“I have entered into the Kingdom of God

353
00:32:45,196 --> 00:32:49,798
and that every action mine is looked
after and guided

354
00:32:49,999 --> 00:32:52,556
by His power and I’m aware of it.

355
00:32:52,757 --> 00:32:56,587
I’m aware that I have entered into
the Kingdom of God

356
00:32:56,788 --> 00:32:59,624
which is expressed through my
collectivity.”

357
00:32:59,825 --> 00:33:04,938
So collectivity is the nature
of a sahaj yogi.

358
00:33:05,922 --> 00:33:09,068
And that’s what one has to realise.

359
00:33:09,269 --> 00:33:12,297
May God bless you all.

360
00:33:12,604 --> 00:33:17,477
Is it all right now? Just time.

361
00:33:20,885 --> 00:33:25,881
How I manage it, without looking
at the watch?

362
00:33:59,586 --> 00:34:02,920
Come forward. There’s some people standing.

