945
01:22:02,000 --> 01:22:06,656
you can’t come to this spiritual
Realisation, or God you could say,

946
01:22:06,857 --> 01:22:09,800
or your Spirit or the truth, you can’t come
to that

947
01:22:10,024 --> 01:22:14,030
on a path which is unrighteous, you can’t
come to that on a path

948
01:22:14,230 --> 01:22:19,762
of unholiness, of immorality, or
of extreme behaviour.

949
01:22:19,964 --> 01:22:23,124
