feel the cool breeze.

954
01:22:32,046 --> 01:22:35,469
When you get Realisation, and anybody
gets it - you don’t have to pay for it -

955
01:22:35,670 --> 01:22:38,973
you feel the cool breeze in your hands
coming from the picture or from Mataji.

956
01:22:39,181 --> 01:22:41,207
As soon as you actually feel, and you have
to verify for yourself,

957
01:22:41,414 --> 01:22:43,993
and you might say “there’s a cool breeze”,
doesn’t make a cool breeze;

958
01:22:44,194 --> 01:22:46,741
but if you feel the cool breeze you can’t
really deny it.

959
01:22:46,942 --> 01:22:49,181
Secondly, you feel cool which comes out
of your head,

960
01:22:49,382 --> 01:22:51,588
when you get Realisation, not before.

961
01:22:51,789 --> 01:22:55,812
Thirdly, you begin to feel all this
extremely subtle, very sensitive

962
01:22:56,013 --> 01:23:00,836
and beautifully made creation which is
the human personality.

963
01:23:01,037 --> 01:23:04,468
You begin to feel its subtleties.
Interviewer: Where does this all lead us?

964
01:23:04,669 --> 01:23:07,662
Where is it going to take us? Yogi: It
takes us into the future, absolutely,

965
01:23:07,863 --> 01:23:11,054
or you could say into the present; it takes
you to yourself.

966
01:23:11,255 --> 01:23:15,551
When the Kundalini goes through the second
to the top chakra - the sixth chakra,

967
01:23:15,752 --> 01:23:17,846
you come into the present and you enter
a state

968
01:23:18,047 --> 01:23:20,570
of thoughtless awareness, spontaneously.
It’s absolutely natural,

969
01:23:20,771 --> 01:23:23,316
it just happens, when the Kundalini
reaches that point.

970
01:23:23,517 --> 01:23:30,599
The reason for that is that, suppose you
are thinking,

971
01:23:30,815 --> 01:23:34,804
you can’t possibly be in the present, you
can’t be aware of the actually present.

972
01:23:35,005 --> 01:23:37,367
You can be aware of just what’s just
passed,

973
01:23:37,568 --> 01:23:39,437
or what’s going to happen in a very short
time,

974
01:23:39,638 --> 01:23:41,885
but you can’t be aware of the absolute
present.

975
01:23:42,086 --> 01:23:45,406
So the only way to be in the present,
absolutely, is to be thoughtless,

976
01:23:45,607 --> 01:23:50,723
and the Kundalini does this, when it
crosses that point on the forehead.

977
01:23:50,924 --> 01:23:54,266
Then you just become thoughtlessly aware
and we are in that state all the time.

978
01:23:54,467 --> 01:23:57,606
All we do is in that state. It sounds
strange, but it’s a reality.

979
01:23:57,807 --> 01:24:00,580
The cares go, the troubles go, your
problems go, as these chakras

980
01:24:00,781 --> 01:24:03,361
get cleared out by the Kundalini rising up,

981
01:24:03,562 --> 01:24:06,319
it clears out all the awful things that
cause the problems;

982
01:24:06,520 --> 01:24:10,245
and you become in the end a joyful being.

