1281
01:46:40,923 --> 01:46:44,212
that ye shall also love one another.

1282
01:46:44,413 --> 01:46:48,628
³⁵By this shall all men know that ye are
my disciples,

1283
01:46:48,829 --> 01:46:52,623
if ye have love one to another.

1284
01:46:52,824 --> 01:46:59,066
³⁶Simon Peter said unto him, Lord, whither
goest thou?

1285
01:46:59,267 --> 01:47:03,200
Jesus answered him, [Whither] I go,

1286
01:47:03,438 --> 01:47:08,661
thou canst not follow me now; but thou
shalt follow me afterwards.

1287
01:47:08,862 --> 01:47:13,559
³⁷Peter said unto him, Lord, why cannot
