1293
01:47:43,563 --> 01:47:45,677
Other yogi: ¹Let not your heart be
troubled:

1294
01:47:45,878 --> 01:47:50,285
 ye believe in God, believe also in me.

1295
01:47:50,512 --> 01:47:54,752
²In my Father’s house are many mansions:

1296
01:47:54,953 --> 01:47:58,399
if it were not so, I would have told you.

