Shri Mataji: Now come.

1403
01:56:36,524 --> 01:56:42,025
John and Don. Yes. Just take it ...

1404
01:56:42,226 --> 01:56:46,923
Gavin:  and that your joy might be full.
Shri Mataji: ... in the bowl.

1405
01:56:47,464 --> 01:56:54,227
¹²This is my commandment, That ye love
one another, as I have loved you.

1406
01:56:57,659 --> 01:57:00,619
¹³Greater love hath no man than this,

1407
01:57:00,820 --> 01:57:05,522
that a man lay down his life for his
friends.

1408
01:57:05,723 --> 01:57:11,644
¹⁴Ye are my friends, if ye do whatsoever
I command you.

1409
01:57:12,804 --> 01:57:15,669
¹⁵Henceforth I call you not servants;

1410
01:57:15,870 --> 01:57:19,674
for the servant knoweth not what his lord
