1413
01:57:41,769 --> 01:57:48,882
Shri Mataji: Rub it hard. Hard. Hm.
Very hard.

1414
01:57:49,083 --> 01:57:52,440
Yogi: ¹⁶Ye have not chosen me, but I have
chosen you,

1415
01:57:52,641 --> 01:57:56,897
and ordained you, that ye should go forth
and bring forth fruit,

1416
01:57:57,098 --> 01:58:01,286
and that your fruit should remain: that
whatsoever ye shall ask

1417
01:58:01,487 --> 01:58:05,629
of the Father in my name, he may give
it to you.

1418
01:58:05,830 --> 01:58:09,848
¹⁷These things I command you, that ye love
one another.

1419
01:58:10,049 --> 01:58:14,360
¹⁸If the world hate you, ye know that it
hated me before it hated you.

1420
01:58:14,561 --> 01:58:17,633
Shri Mataji: Throughout one Commandment.
Just see. Because He knew

1421
01:58:17,834 --> 01:58:22,487
that if you don’t love each other, nobody
is going to believe you.

1422
01:58:23,226 --> 01:58:28,595
Yogi: ¹⁹If ye were of the world, the world
would love his own:

1423
01:58:28,806 --> 01:58:33,428
but because ye are not of the world, but
I have chosen you out of the world,

1424
01:58:33,636 --> 01:58:36,916
therefore the world hateth you.

1425
01:58:37,117 --> 01:58:39,832
²⁰Remember the word that I said unto you,

1426
01:58:40,033 --> 01:58:43,273
The servant is not greater than his lord.

1427
01:58:43,474 --> 01:58:48,205
If they have persecuted me, they will also
persecute you;

1428
01:58:48,407 --> 01:58:53,569
if they have kept my saying, they will
keep yours also.

1429
01:58:53,770 --> 01:58:58,524
²¹But all these things will they do unto
you for my name’s sake,

1430
01:58:58,744 --> 01:59:02,095
because they know not him that sent me.

1431
01:59:02,296 --> 01:59:08,932
²²If I had not come and spoken unto them,
they had not had sin…

1432
01:59:09,133 --> 01:59:13,201
Shri Mataji: They had…?
