1434
01:59:18,406 --> 01:59:22,379
²³He that hateth me hateth my Father also.

1435
01:59:22,580 --> 01:59:27,089
²⁴If I had not done among them the works
which none other man did,

1436
01:59:27,314 --> 01:59:34,795
they had not had sin: but now have they
both

1437
01:59:35,025 --> 01:59:39,160
seen and hated both me and my Father.

1438
01:59:39,361 --> 01:59:41,286
But this cometh to pass,

1439
01:59:41,487 --> 01:59:45,094
that the word might be fulfilled that
is written in their law,

1440
01:59:45,319 --> 01:59:53,217
They hated me without a cause.
Shri Mataji: See. Very true.

1441
01:59:53,649 --> 01:59:58,499
Yogi: ²⁶But when the Comforter is come,
whom I will send unto you from the Father,

1442
01:59:58,700 --> 02:00:02,733
even the Spirit of truth, which proceedeth
from the Father,

