then testify, you can testify.

1445
02:00:13,404 --> 02:00:15,984
Yogi: ²⁷And ye also shall bear witness,

1446
02:00:16,185 --> 02:00:19,666
because ye have been with me from
the beginning.

1447
02:00:19,867 --> 02:00:22,863
Shri Mataji: From the very beginning.

