02:00:45,269 --> 02:00:52,947
Just keep it steady. Absolutely. Steady it.

1452
02:00:53,190 --> 02:00:55,836
Yogi: ¹These things have I spoken unto you,
Shri Mataji: You still you are moving.

1453
02:00:56,036 --> 02:00:58,193
Yogi: that ye should not be offended.

1454
02:00:58,394 --> 02:01:02,204
²They shall put you out of the synagogues:
yea, the time cometh,

1455
02:01:02,405 --> 02:01:05,444
that whosoever killeth you will think that
he doeth God service.

1456
02:01:05,645 --> 02:01:08,232
[Shri Mataji: “Better. Put your hands
towards me.”] Yogi: ³And these things will

1457
02:01:08,433 --> 02:01:12,329
they do unto you, because they have not
